## Auto-Submit on Complete

```typescript
@Component({
  template: `
    <sng-otp-input
      name="verification-code"
      [(value)]="otpCode"
      [maxLength]="6"
      (complete)="verifyCode($event)"
    >
      <!-- slots -->
    </sng-otp-input>
  `
