### Dashboard metrics

```ts
type DashboardMetric = {
  id: 'open-prs' | 'incidents' | 'deployments' | 'team-online';
  label: string;
  value: number;
  deltaText?: string;
  status?: 'healthy' | 'warning' | 'critical';
};
```

